{"tid":1078142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[不過上網要翻牆] 林鄭：大灣區有望成矽谷加華爾街","createTime":"2019-03-26T05:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T09:12:14.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5a703b55c68b34e67ddb7573a7998a1e6ea4c1ac","tid":1078142,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:50:51.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥在北京出席中國發展高層論壇，形容粵港澳大灣區有望成為「矽谷加華爾街」，廣東省省長馬興瑞則指三地制度仍有差距，會與特首合力營造「軟環境」。<br />\n<br />\n在中國發展高層論壇上粵港澳三地的領導齊集，談大灣區發展，行政長官林鄭月娥以英文發言，廣東省省長馬興瑞則指會完善交通網絡，努力促進一小時內到達大灣區內各主要城市，但比起硬件及基礎設施，「軟環境」要更加改善，又指三地政府當務之急是要改善人才流動。"},{"pid":"766bbba67d2cf8212ee822deb433f54c8d33c52b","tid":1078142,"uid":12824,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:54:18.000Z","msg":"乜柒嘢叫軟環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲係咩中文嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed0ef0c9a423a4b37bd5893b929988172a9b73c","tid":1078142,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"766bbba67d2cf8212ee822deb433f54c8d33c52b","tid":1078142,"uid":12824,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:54:18.000Z","msg":"乜柒嘢叫軟環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲係咩中文嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:58:58.000Z","msg":"我寧願佢用英文講好過<br />\n不撚知所謂"},{"pid":"e8b68f05ae1f757f468bb85e749adb87eeb70cf5","tid":1078142,"uid":239205,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:01:58.000Z","msg":"alan!alex!"},{"pid":"cf365be0794fb2afdec2c10535c956f86535ac2a","tid":1078142,"uid":202131,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"766bbba67d2cf8212ee822deb433f54c8d33c52b","tid":1078142,"uid":12824,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:54:18.000Z","msg":"乜柒嘢叫軟環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲係咩中文嚟<img src=\"/assets/fac